    "synopsis": "Garviel Loken, the last loyalist of the broken Mournival, comes back from a secret errand to Caliban at Malcador the Sigillite's bidding and goes to ground in a long-abandoned bio-dome on Luna. Battered by betrayal and bewildered by a galaxy he no longer recognises, he is visited there by his dead brother Tarik Torgaddon — laughing, irreverent, exactly as he was — and cannot tell whether it is a fractured mind speaking back to itself, or whether the dead really do walk on the Mendax side of the Moon. A quiet, melancholic interlude that bridges Loken's resurrection and his return to the war for Terra.",
